## What Gets Detected

### AI Agents & Coding Tools (16 processes)

| Tool | Process Name |
|------|-------------|
| Interview Coder | `interviewcoder.exe` |
| Cluely | `cluely.exe`, `cluely_helper.exe` |
| ParakeetAI | `pmodule.exe` |
| LockedIn AI | `ghost.exe` |
| ChatGPT Desktop | `chatgpt.exe` |
| Claude Desktop | `claude.exe` |
| Cursor | `cursor.exe` |
| GitHub Copilot | `copilot.exe` |
| Windsurf | `windsurf.exe` |
| Google Gemini | `gemini.exe` |
| MS Copilot Proxy | `mscopilot_proxy.exe` |
| Chegg | `chegg.exe` |
| Brainly | `brainly.exe` |
| Photomath | `photomath.exe` |
| Socratic | `socratic.exe` |
| Suspicious Electron | `electron.exe` (flagged as potential AI overlay) |

### AI API Network Connections (12 domains)

`api.openai.com` В· `api.anthropic.com` В· `generativelanguage.googleapis.com` В· `api.groq.com` В· `api.cohere.ai` В· `api.mistral.ai` В· `api.perplexity.ai` В· `api.together.xyz` В· `api.replicate.com` В· `api.deepseek.com` В· `api.fireworks.ai` В· `api.x.ai`

### Command-Line Pattern Detection (13 patterns)

Inspects process command-line arguments for: `openai`, `anthropic`, `chatgpt`, `claude`, `gemini`, `copilot`, `codewhisperer`, `gpt-4`, `gpt4`, `llama`, `--ai-`, `--model`, `huggingface`

### Remote Access Tools (16 processes)

AnyDesk В· TeamViewer В· Chrome Remote Desktop В· VNC Server/Viewer В· UltraViewer В· Parsec В· RustDesk В· Ammyy Admin В· Supremo В· Splashtop В· LogMeIn В· BeyondTrust В· ScreenConnect

### Screen Share / Meeting Apps (13 processes)

Zoom В· Microsoft Teams В· Slack В· Skype В· Discord В· Cisco Webex В· GoToMeeting В· join.me В· BlueJeans В· Zhumu В· **Quick Assist** В· Samsung Quick Share В· Zoom Capture Host

### Screen Recorders (15 processes)

OBS Studio (32/64-bit) В· Streamlabs В· Camtasia В· Snagit В· Bandicam В· vMix В· XSplit В· Screencastify В· Loom В· ShareX В· ScreenPal В· Screenpresso В· Kazam В· SimpleScreenRecorder В· FFmpeg

### Browser Extensions (26 extensions)

**AI Assistants:** Monica AI В· ChatGPT for Google В· UseChatGPT В· Merlin В· Sider AI В· MaxAI В· Copilot Bing В· Phind В· Perplexity AI

**Cheating Tools:** Brainly В· Chegg В· CourseHero В· Bartleby

**Writing AI:** Grammarly AI В· QuillBot В· Copy AI В· Jasper AI

**Screen Capture:** Screencastify В· Loom В· GoFullPage В· Scribe

**Remote Access:** Chrome Remote Desktop В· AnyDesk

Scans Chrome, Edge, and Brave (all profiles).

---

## Credibility Scoring

Every event affects the session's credibility score (starts at 100):

| Score Range | Verdict | Meaning |
|-------------|---------|---------|
| 90вҖ“100 | `CLEAR` | No significant issues |
| 70вҖ“89 | `UNDER_REVIEW` | Minor issues detected |
| 50вҖ“69 | `SUSPICIOUS` | Multiple violations |
| 0вҖ“49 | `FLAGGED` | Strong evidence of cheating |

### Event Severity Levels

| Severity | Default Penalty | Example |
|----------|----------------|---------|
| `CRITICAL` | -15 | AI agent detected, remote access, hidden window |
| `HIGH` | -10 | Tab switch, clipboard, AI cmdline pattern |
| `MEDIUM` | -5 | Gaze away, loud audio, screen resize |
| `LOW` | -2 | Right-click attempt |

Compounding penalties apply when 3+ events occur within 5 minutes (configurable).

